lead_paragraph: Mirza Teletovic scored 26 points off the bench, P.J. Tucker added 24 and the Phoenix Suns dealt another blow to the Houston Rockets' dwindling playoff chances with a 124-115 victory on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Suns End 7-Game Skid With 124-115 Win Over Rockets
